{"tid":583324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴暫緩解僱車長　葉蔚琳：正義必然長存","createTime":"2018-03-07T01:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T09:46:06.000Z","uid":70985,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a083fc767adce56767b270b65659ababed4abdb3","tid":583324,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T01:44:07.000Z","msg":"上月24日發起罷駛行動爭取資方改善員工權益的「九巴月薪車長大聯盟」召集人葉蔚琳，連同參與罷駛的丈夫劉卓恒和另外兩名車長，昨天分別接到九巴發出終止僱用通知，原定今日生效。不過葉蔚琳及另外兩名代表，凌晨與九巴高層會面一個多小時後，九巴宣布暫緩終止僱用決定，並盡快啟動覆檢機制。<br />\n<br />\n葉蔚琳會後形容「正義必然長存，真理永遠得到支持」，她和公司也拿出了最大誠意。她又說，4人可先取回職員證，而之前向公司提出的3個訴求，包括取消車長評核機制等，很大機會6月達成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180307/s00001/1520378919282\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180307%2Fs00001%2F1520378919282&d=ZFb6EgCh8lAR4UKiz3kEXZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=ebf94dac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180307%2Fs00001%2F1520378919282&h=1317b1fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180307/s00001/1520378919282</a><br />\n<br />\n彈出又彈入九巴管理層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd37d0eea21efa492e2e40d53748a1ce68eb22f2","tid":583324,"uid":102096,"like":8,"dislike":21,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T01:45:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f63b1f5f71cc3664939b4c7ba6eec3ebd4d7d021","tid":583324,"uid":103127,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T01:48:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b05a3e7f2c0243263868c76169bf081f95b78929","tid":583324,"uid":39245,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T01:51:42.000Z","msg":"狗巴彈弓手真係好撚柒, 炒啦屌你老母, 與民為敵啦"},{"pid":"7b082196f05304388d0625f759f6e390c9c85bf0","tid":583324,"uid":70985,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T01:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src